




{"id":11173,"date":"2022-07-27T10:06:28","date_gmt":"2022-07-27T03:06:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=11173"},"modified":"2024-03-26T22:16:17","modified_gmt":"2024-03-26T15:16:17","slug":"tu-quan-ly-chia-khoa-thong-minh-an-ninh-cho-ban","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tu-quan-ly-chia-khoa-thong-minh-an-ninh-cho-ban\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ee6 QU\u1ea2N L\u00dd CH\u00ccA KHO\u00c1 TH\u00d4NG MINH &#8211; AN NINH CHO B\u1ea0N"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_78 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tu-quan-ly-chia-khoa-thong-minh-an-ninh-cho-ban\/#tu_quan_ly_chia_khoa_thong_minh_la_gi\" >T\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tu-quan-ly-chia-khoa-thong-minh-an-ninh-cho-ban\/#tai_sao_phai_su_dung_he_thong_tu_quan_ly_chia_khoa_thong_minh\" >T\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng minh?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y kho\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed \u1edf kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi an ninh t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n doanh nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 v\u1eadt l\u00fd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00f4ng ty.<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u1eeba v\u00e0 nh\u1ecf, khi ngu\u1ed3n ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u00f2n eo h\u1eb9p. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng v\u00ec c\u00f3 kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Do \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kho\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed tr\u00ean quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m.Tuy v\u1eady, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a v\u1eadt l\u00fd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u00edch h\u1ee3p ho\u1eb7c ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t tho\u00e1t kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><em>T\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 g\u00ec? \u00c1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong qu\u1ea3n l\u00ed t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay\u00a0<\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11174 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/LAndwell-709x400.jpg\" alt=\"H\u1ec6 TH\u1ed0NG T\u1ee6 QU\u1ea2N L\u00dd CH\u00ccA KHO\u00c1 TH\u00d4NG MINH\" width=\"709\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/LAndwell-709x400.jpg 709w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/LAndwell-768x433.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/LAndwell-600x339.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/LAndwell.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 709px) 100vw, 709px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u tr\u1eef an to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng?<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a?<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y ra m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n th\u00edch h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng? B\u1ea1n lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a b\u1ecb chia s\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t?<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a?<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>C\u00e1c t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n th\u1ea5t tho\u00e1t \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c th\u00f4ng qua t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tu_quan_ly_chia_khoa_thong_minh_la_gi\"><\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/m.antoanthongtin.vn\/tieu-chuan---chat-luong\/tieu-chuan-quoc-gia-viet-nam-ve-quan-ly-khoa-100084\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">T\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh INNO l\u00e0 m\u1ecd\u0302t h\u1eb9\u0302 th\u00f4\u0301ng qua\u0309n ly\u0301 chi\u0300a kho\u0301a co\u031b \u0111i\u1eb9\u0302n, cung c\u00e2\u0301p gia\u0309i pha\u0301p plug &amp; play d\u00ea\u0303 da\u0300ng cho ngu\u031b\u01a1\u0300i du\u0300ng, giu\u0301p ti\u00ea\u0301t ki\u1eb9\u0302m th\u01a1\u0300i gian va\u0300 tra\u0301nh ca\u0301c r\u0103\u0301c r\u00f4\u0301i khi pha\u0309i tua\u0302n theo ca\u0301c hu\u031b\u01a1\u0301ng d\u00e2\u0303n ca\u0300i \u0111\u1ea1\u0306t ph\u01b0\u0301c ta\u0323p. M\u00f4\u0303i kho\u0301a \u0111u\u031b\u01a1\u0323c gia\u0301m sa\u0301t \u0111u\u031b\u01a1\u0323c g\u0103\u0301n vi\u0303nh vi\u00ea\u0303n va\u0300o ca\u0301c key tag. G\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p Plug and Play \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 RFID ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn<\/li>\n<li>Giao di\u1ec7n m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Android<\/li>\n<li>Truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a b\u00ean trong t\u1ee7 qua v\u00e2n tay, m\u00e3 PIN, th\u1ebb RFID<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn an to\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng th\u1ebb RFID v\u00e0 v\u00f2ng ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng b\u00ean trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Android gi\u00fap l\u01b0u c\u00e1c t\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a g\u00f3i thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp<\/li>\n<li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00ean t\u01b0\u1eddng an to\u00e0n<\/li>\n<li>Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi pin d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ecdn<a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/thiet-bi-cho-truong-hoc-thong-minh\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11175 size-medium\" style=\"caret-color: #555555; color: #555555;\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell1-800x358.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh Landwell\" width=\"800\" height=\"358\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell1-800x358.jpg 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell1-768x344.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell1-600x269.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell1.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai_sao_phai_su_dung_he_thong_tu_quan_ly_chia_khoa_thong_minh\"><\/span>T\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng minh?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng minh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kh\u00f3a th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ghi ch\u00e9p th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n: Ch\u00fang l\u01b0u tr\u1eef v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i kh\u00f3a m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng qua t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch.<\/p>\n<h3>Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh INNO<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>18 khe c\u1eafm ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng, v\u1eefng ch\u1eafn, tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng kh\u00f3a an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u1ebb RFID<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n seal b\u1ed5 sung gi\u1eefa ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a v\u00e0 m\u00f3c kh\u00f3a<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n truy c\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c kh\u00f3a nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb vi\u00ean qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00e1c quy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ec1n truy c\u1eadp<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u1eadt k\u00fd s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/li>\n<li>B\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u khi ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111a ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/li>\n<li>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Android v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ki\u1ec3m tra, theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 b\u00e1o c\u00e1o c\u00e1c kh\u00f3a ho\u1eb7c nh\u00f3m kh\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t b\u00e1o c\u00e1o qua giao di\u1ec7n USB.<\/li>\n<li>B\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ee9c th\u00ec trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p l\u1ea5y ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ea3 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a qu\u00e1 h\u1ea1n, k\u00e8m \u0111\u00e8n LED \u1edf khe c\u1eafm v\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh<\/li>\n<li>M\u1edf kho\u00e1 kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-11179 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell2-800x333.jpg\" alt=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh Landwell\" width=\"668\" height=\"278\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell2-800x333.jpg 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell2-768x320.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell2-600x250.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/landwell2.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" \/><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 c\u0169ng cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c, bao g\u1ed3m:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u chi ph\u00ed: H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1c kh\u00f3a lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea1ch to\u00e1n. Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed h\u00e0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u00e1c ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a b\u1ecb thi\u1ebfu, v\u00ec v\u1eady n\u0103ng su\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n cao. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0, c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3n l\u1ed7 ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u00f4ng th\u1eddi ch\u00ed ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ban \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 do \u0111\u00f3, chi ph\u00ed ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m theo.<\/li>\n<li>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd r\u1ee7i ro t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n: H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kh\u00f3a duy tr\u00ec nh\u1eadt k\u00fd giao d\u1ecbch, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 k\u00edn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ai \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f3a n\u00e0o khi n\u00e0o. Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a m\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu.<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh: H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kh\u00f3a cho ph\u00e9p ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd h\u01a1n c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f3a trong c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. V\u00ed d\u1ee5: b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ca l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ec7nh gi\u1edbi nghi\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 cho ph\u00e9p nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 cho c\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 th\u00f4ng minh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kh\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a an to\u00e0n. N\u00f3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u xem m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng minh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n cho t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng? H\u00e3y <a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/lien-he\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/a> ngay v\u1edbi INNO \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y kho\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed \u1edf kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi an ninh t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n doanh nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00eca kho\u00e1 v\u1eadt l\u00fd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00f4ng ty&#8230;.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":11175,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-11173","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11173","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11173"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11173\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":15526,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11173\/revisions\/15526"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/11175"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11173"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=11173"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=11173"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}